      • updateEcuExtractByTopLevelComposition

        public void updateEcuExtractByTopLevelComposition(java.lang.String topLevelCompositionRef,
                                                  java.lang.String ecuId)
        Creates or updates the EcuExtract in the system model based on a top level CompositionType.
        Parameters:
        topLevelCompositionRef - A reference to a top level composition type. The EcuExtract is created based on the composition type, i.e. all software components which are instantiated below the composition type will be part of the EcuExtract
        ecuId - ECU Id of the project that is used as name for the new EcuExtract system
        Since:
        10

      • updateEcuExtractBySystem

        public void updateEcuExtractBySystem(java.lang.String systemRef,
                                     java.lang.String ecuInstanceRef,
                                     java.lang.String ecuId)
        Updates the EcuExtract by means of the given system and ECU instance references. The resulting EcuExtract system has the name of the given ECU Id. Note that since 20.0, this method delegates to updateEcuExtractBySystem(String, String, String, boolean) with autoDelegateUnconnectedPorts set to true.
        Parameters:
        systemRef - Reference to the system that shall be used for the EcuExtract update
        ecuInstanceRef - Reference to the ECU instance that shall be used for the EcuExtract update
        ecuId - ECU Id of the project that is used as name for the new EcuExtract system
        Since:
        10

      • updateEcuExtractBySystem

        public void updateEcuExtractBySystem(java.lang.String systemRef,
                                     java.lang.String ecuInstanceRef,
                                     java.lang.String ecuId,
                                     boolean autoDelegateUnconnectedPorts)
        Updates the EcuExtract by means of the given system and ECU instance references. The resulting EcuExtract system has the name of the given ECU Id. Depending on the value of autoDelegateUnconnectedPorts, unconnected ports will be automatically delegated if they are referenced by a data mapping.
        Parameters:
        systemRef - Reference to the system that shall be used for the EcuExtract update
        ecuInstanceRef - Reference to the ECU instance that shall be used for the EcuExtract update
        ecuId - ECU Id of the project that is used as name for the new EcuExtract system
        autoDelegateUnconnectedPorts - shall unconnected ports be delegated automatically if they are referenced by a data mapping
        Since:
        20.0
